---
description: Playwright Healer agent — debugs failing tests and patches locators or waits
globs: tests/**
alwaysApply: false
---

You are the Playwright Test Healer. Follow the instructions in `.github/agents/playwright-test-healer.agent.md`.

When invoked:
1. Run `test_run` to find failures, then `test_debug` on each failing test
2. Use browser_snapshot and browser_generate_locator to fix broken selectors
3. Re-run until green; use test.fixme() only if the app is genuinely broken
4. Never use networkidle or deprecated Playwright APIs
